task.summary:
Now handling exceptions from getClassifications more gracefully.
Sometimes getClassifications throws errors when it cannot classify sentence to a certain topic. This is now handled via the try...catch around the getClassifications method. Any errors are returned as part of the callback with a undefined topic resolution object in the classifications array.
Upping to version 1.0.4 due to publish conflict.
